<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] An Istanbul State Security Court has ordered the 
withdrawal of the 25th issue of NOKTA magazine from circulation 
because it makes propaganda for the illegal Islamic Great 
Eastern Raiders Front. 

</TEXT>

