<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Strasbourg, June 20 (AFP) -- Swedish parliamentarian 
Daniel Tarschys took the reins of the 32-nation Council of 
Europe on Monday [20 June], replacing France's Catherine 
Lalumiere as secretary general, the organisation said. 
  The Liberal Party MP was elected last month by the Council's 
