<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   WEU Council To Hold Emergency Meeting on Rwanda </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    WEU Council To Hold Emergency Meeting on Rwanda </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1706095894 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 0929 GMT 17 
