<F P=102>   PM1706110294 London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH in English 17 Jun 94 
p 1 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM1706110294 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
