<H3> <TI>   AN To Oppose Legislative Solution to `Bribesville' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    AN To Oppose Legislative Solution to `Bribesville' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2006131294 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1029 GMT 18 
Jun 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2006131294 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
