<H3> <TI>   Bern Submits `Improved' Offer on WTO Headquarters </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bern Submits `Improved' Offer on WTO Headquarters </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1606103094 Bern ATSA/SDAA Database in French 1550 GMT 15 
Jun 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1606103094 </F>
