<H3> <TI>   Ministry Announces Supplemental Budget </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministry Announces Supplemental Budget </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2006174894 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1650 GMT 
20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2006174894 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>
<F P=105>  Italian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] "The job of improving public finances will be done 
with a mini-budget which will have effects on this year's 
deficit and on the 1995 accounts," a communique of the Treasury 
said. It also analyzed the "turbulence on the financial 
markets." 
  "To this uncertain climate have been added some internal 
developments which may increase public expenses. However, these 
will be balanced by special measures aimed at bringing more 
money to the state," the communique added. 

</TEXT>

