  [Text] Finance Minister Faidhros Oikonomidhis resumed his 
duties today following an absence caused by the heart attack he 
suffered on 2 April. Mr. Oikonomidhis called on President 
Glavkos Kliridhis before resuming his duties. Responding to a 
