<F P=102> TA1806151794 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1200 
GMT 18 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1806151794 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] A bomb exploded in the cargo department of a travel 
agency in Kadikoy, Istanbul, causing material damage. No one 
was killed or injured in the incident. 
  An explosion occurred around 0945 this morning in the cargo 
department of a travel agency on Kadikoy's Rihtim Street. The 
explosion shattered the glass and triggered a fire. 
Firefighters extinguished the fire before it spread any further. 
  Officials reported that a bus left for Harem shortly before 
the explosion and a bag believed to have been forgotten by the 
passengers was taken to the cargo department. Officials noted 
that a bomb which was inside the bag exploded and that a 
27-28-year-old- woman, who is believed to have left the bag, is 
being sought. 

</TEXT>

