<F P=100> AUSTRIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Supreme Court Overrules Verdict on Neo-Nazi Kuessel </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Supreme Court Overrules Verdict on Neo-Nazi Kuessel </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2206104194 Vienna DIE PRESSE in German 22 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> AU2206104194 </F>
<F P=104>  Vienna DIE PRESSE </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [APA report: "Verdict for Kuessel Overruled"] </F>
  [Text] Vienna -- The Supreme Court of Justice partly set 
aside the verdict on the neo-Nazi leader Gottfried Kuessel 
yesterday. The founder of the "Extraparliamentary Opposition 
Loyal to the People" was sentenced to 10 years imprisonment for 
illegal National Socialist activities. 
  The judges ruled that the directions to the jury regarding 
individual charges were insufficient. A new trial is now 
necessary, and a new verdict must be passed. 

</TEXT>

